          </section>

          <section id="alternatives">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-5">9. When none of the three fits \u2014 QR, WiFi RTT, UWB</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
