            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4 italic">Sources: IDTechEx 2024 RAIN RFID Forecasts; Bluetooth SIG 2024 Annual Market Update; NFC Forum 2025 Annual Report; RFIDAK 2026 published price book.</p>
